      <title>英镑上涨，因就业市场强劲迹象无视降息预期</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-13/pound-gains-as-signs-of-robust-jobs-market-defy-rate-cut-bets</link>
      <description><![CDATA[有迹象表明英国就业市场强劲，英镑上涨，使人们对英国央行今年是否会再降息两次的预期产生怀疑。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-13/pound-gains-as-signs-of-robust-jobs-market-defy-rate-cut-bets</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 13 Aug 2024 07:16:23 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>东京削减债券销售计划 反映利率紧张情绪</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-13/tokyo-cuts-bond-issuance-plan-in-sign-of-interest-rate-jitters</link>
      <description><![CDATA[东京都政府计划本财年削减债券销售，这再次表明日本信贷市场正准备应对央行加息后投资者对债务的需求减弱。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-13/tokyo-cuts-bond-issuance-plan-in-sign-of-interest-rate-jitters</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 13 Aug 2024 06:56:51 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
